{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.280", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.520", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "20.840", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir debattieren heute zum ersten Mal in dieser Legislaturperiode \u00fcber die Fortschreibung der Streitwertgrenze bei der Nichtzulassungsbeschwerde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "20.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.000", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Kollegin von der FDP hat eben aber zu Recht gesagt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.280", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir das nicht zum ersten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.400", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern zum wiederholten Mal diskutieren; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.720", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn mit der Einf\u00fchrung der Nichtzulassungsbeschwerde im Jahre 2002\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.560", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zum 1.\u00a0Januar 2002 ist sie eingef\u00fchrt worden\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.400", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir auch eine Streitwertgrenze in H\u00f6he von 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro eingef\u00fchrt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.360", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diese Regelung ist \u00fcber die Jahre von den unterschiedlichen Koalitionen regelm\u00e4\u00dfig verl\u00e4ngert worden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.000", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen von der FDP, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.240", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "auch die christlich-liberale Koalition ab 2009 hat die Streitwertgrenze bei 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro beibehalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil wir es f\u00fcr richtig gehalten haben."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.240", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.080", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "59.200", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "59.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.280", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Streitwertgrenze hat sich \u00fcber die Jahre bew\u00e4hrt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.760", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie deckt sich auch mit den Regelungen in \u00a7\u00a0522 ZPO, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.880", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in denen es zum Beispiel um die Beschwerde gegen die nicht zugelassene Berufung geht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.480", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch hier gibt es eine Streitwertgrenze in H\u00f6he von 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.520", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Daneben m\u00fcssen wir feststellen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.960", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch in der Praxis hat sie sich bew\u00e4hrt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.320", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von daher ist es richtig, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.520", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.040", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir halten an der Streitwertgrenze in H\u00f6he von 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "91.760", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie sie in der EGZPO geregelt ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "91.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.080", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "fest."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.000", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man wird in den Beratungen aber sicherlich \u00fcber einige Punkte diskutieren k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.600", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.120", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass der vorgelegte Gesetzentwurf das eine oder andere noch offenl\u00e4sst. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.280", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht k\u00f6nnte man auch einmal nach handwerklichen Fehlern schauen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.440", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sprechen zum Beispiel nicht von zweieinhalb Jahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "110.000", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern von eineinhalb Jahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "110.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "111.720", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn ich den Entwurf richtig gelesen habe."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "111.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "118.000", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es geht n\u00e4mlich um den Zeitraum vom 1.\u00a0Juli 2018 bis zum 31.\u00a0Dezember 2019. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "118.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.200", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Diesen handwerklichen Fehler m\u00fcsste man also noch beseitigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "124.080", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir k\u00f6nnten daneben auch dar\u00fcber diskutieren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "124.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.440", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob wir bei der Berechnung des Streitwertes nicht auch noch das eine oder andere Problem l\u00f6sen m\u00fcssen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "133.160", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist n\u00e4mlich sehr schwer zu berechnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "133.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.480", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob die Streitwertgrenze, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.240", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man in G\u00e4nze in die Revision geht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.160", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "erreicht wird. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "140.920", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man kann sich die Frage stellen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "140.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.920", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ob es M\u00f6glichkeiten gibt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.440", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "hier eine Vereinfachung der Berechnung des Streitwertes zu erreichen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.840", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sodass Klarheit f\u00fcr die Rechtsuchenden und die Anw\u00e4lte geschaffen wird und sie bei der Streitwertberechnung nicht nach Gestaltungsm\u00f6glichkeiten suchen m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.200", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "um \u00fcber die 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro zu kommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.760", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch das Thema \u201eAnspruch auf rechtliches Geh\u00f6r\u201c sollten wir in den Beratungen diskutieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.240", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich glaube, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.080", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir k\u00f6nnen auch beim Gesetz insgesamt dar\u00fcber diskutieren: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.000", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie sieht es denn mit den Verl\u00e4ngerungszeitr\u00e4umen aus?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "173.200", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sollten jetzt schauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "173.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.800", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir die alte Regelung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.880", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deren Geltungsdauer mit Termin vom 30.\u00a0Juni dieses Jahres ausl\u00e4uft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.120", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "vern\u00fcnftig in eine Nachfolgeregelung \u00fcberf\u00fchren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.360", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber dann werden wir sicherlich auch mit den Vertretern von Gerichten in eine Diskussion dar\u00fcber kommen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "187.520", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie wir die Regelung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "187.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.640", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "deren G\u00fcltigkeit wir jetzt seit dem Jahr\u00a02002 fortschreiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.680", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in Zukunft gestalten wollen? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.440", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielleicht gibt es da, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.520", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn man mit dem einen oder anderen Richter in einen Dialog einsteigt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.320", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "eine endg\u00fcltige Regelung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "201.320", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dazu m\u00fcssen wir aber alle bereit sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "201.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "202.160", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Von daher glaube ich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "202.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "206.960", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass im Gesetzgebungsverfahren eine vern\u00fcnftige Regelung gefunden werden kann. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "206.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "207.840", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich w\u00fcnsche mir, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "207.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.360", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir so ein Thema nicht zum Streitpunkt werden lassen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.080", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern gemeinsam \u00fcber alle Fraktionen hinweg eine kluge Regelung finden und hier eine ausgewogene Norm im Sinne der revisionsrechtlichen \u00dcberpr\u00fcfung eines einheitlichen Revisionsrechts mit einem Streitwert ab 20\u00a0000\u00a0Euro, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "219.080", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "bei dem wir bleiben sollten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "219.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.040", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in diesem Bundestag verabschieden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.840", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn es denn dazu kommt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.720", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Danke sch\u00f6n."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.960", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.000", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dr.\u00a0Sensburg.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.280", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Damit schlie\u00dfe ich die Aussprache."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.040", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Interfraktionell wird \u00dcberweisung des Gesetzentwurfs auf Drucksache\u00a019/1686 an den Ausschuss f\u00fcr Recht und Verbraucherschutz vorgeschlagen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "230.480", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich gehe davon aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "230.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.680", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es keine anderweitigen Vorschl\u00e4ge gibt.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "232.960", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann ist die \u00dcberweisung so beschlossen."
   ]
  }
 ]
}